snippet.title: DO NOT - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
DO NOT will be released on December 20 is free for the first 24 hours 
DO NOT a FIRST PERSON ANALOG HORROR VIDEOGAME
The game is currently in an Early Access phase!

Download DO NOT: https://docetgames.itch.io/do-not

Do Not is an analog horror game set in a '90s donut fast food restaurant. You're the night shift worker at a Donut&Go on the outskirts of town. Few customers, lots of silence... but try not to die of fright!

Do Not is our very first project. In the future, we plan to design new modes or enhance the game experience with more updates.


©2024 Docet Games Studio.
